    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects with chronic terminal nephropathy under hemodialysis treatment for at least 3
             months

          -  Signed informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with chronic terminal nephropathy previously treated with peritoneal dialysis

          -  Receptors of a renal graft

          -  Patients with malignant neoplastic conditions

          -  Pregnant women
      </textblock>
